WEBVTT

1
01:32:13.280 --> 01:32:15.410 
罗德  快打给报社
You'll never get away with it. Call the papers.

2
01:32:15.660 --> 01:32:17.410 
换成是我  我就不会这么做
I wouldn't do that if I were you.

3
01:32:17.660 --> 01:32:19.710 
你无权指使我该怎么做  琳娜
Don't tell me what to do, Lina.

4
01:32:19.960 --> 01:32:23.420 
难道你把我当成傻子不成
What do you think I am, dumb or something?

5
01:32:23.670 --> 01:32:26.750 
我已叫律师把合约看过一遍
I had my lawyer go over my contract.

6
01:32:27.000 --> 01:32:28.130 
合约
Contract?

7
01:32:28.380 --> 01:32:31.590 
我的宣传由我控制  不是你
And I control my publicity, not you.

8
01:32:31.800 --> 01:32:35.510 
电影公司必须对所有关于我的文宣负责
The studio is responsible for every word printed about me.

9
01:32:35.720 --> 01:32:38.850 
如果不满意  我可以起诉
If I don't like it, I can sue.

10
01:32:39.100 --> 01:32:40.180 
什么
What?

11
01:32:40.390 --> 01:32:42.640 
我可以起诉
I can sue.

12
01:32:42.850 --> 01:32:45.770 
如果你告诉报社有关凯希·莎登的事
If you tell the papers about Kathy Selden

